{"tid":2118710,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警員指明: 「拉黃衫嘅」","createTime":"2020-07-21T15:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T16:08:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1d647189263c74b2f8d5a137c4b17d140ce6b38c","tid":2118710,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/appledailyhk/5235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fappledailyhk%2F5235&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=4b3cbb84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/appledailyhk/5235</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警察針對記者成為常態。今晚7.21元朗恐襲一周年，大批防暴警在晚上8時已在Yoho Mall商場內包圍並截查記者。<br />\n<br />\n警察要求現場記者「除罩對樣」、搜袋，並抄錄身份證資料，容貌被警攝錄機拍下。有近20名網媒及大學記者更被發出限聚令告票。<br />\n<br />\n而在晚上10點，在Yoho Mall外的鳳琴街有大批防暴警駐守，警員命令所有在場傳媒企成一排接受截查。有警員恐嚇在場記者需停止直播及拍攝。當時蘋果包括直播記者以及採訪記者亦被截查。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果記者被放行不久後，在不足10分鐘的時間，與另一班正在離開現場的記者及區議員再次被防暴警截查。有被發限聚令告票的記者表示，聽到警員指明「拉黃衫嘅」。"},{"pid":"9e2144df69e2d3ad509807a38526014e3ae31240","tid":2118710,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cee90d0b064897859534d69cc5e7870b00ecc7","tid":2118710,"uid":148262,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"原來警察拉人真係睇顏色的<br />\nAlways yellow objects"},{"pid":"7597643bb49b4c41e33dbc13c96492e37d813425","tid":2118710,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e2144df69e2d3ad509807a38526014e3ae31240","tid":2118710,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h